*Laku* noć (Good night).
*Lakše* je reći nego uraditi (It is easier to say than do).
*Laku* noc, sretno! (Good night, good luck!).
*Lakše* je biti bogat nego siromašan (It is easier to be rich than poor).
*Lakše* je pronaći izlaz iz teških situacija (It is easier to find a way out of difficult situations).